title: Missing the Rose
author: chickenprime
pages:
#- Dear NL

It brings me great sadness to leave, but I am through with DiamondReapers torment and injustice.

I will miss you boll, bluwolf, and galvan.You are all great guys.
Dont change.

#- In loving memory,
Chickenprime, the man that wanted to be communist.
